strings.Value: "I can't stop thinking about that woman, the Defaced Sister! So fascinating — both she herself, and her magic. I wish I could find out more from her..."
"She fills me with unease. One who tells the truth has no need to hide their face. One who hides their face hides something else as well."
"To hide one's face and to reject one's very name — all in service to a higher power... Such a fascinating and dignified idea. I must think on this further..."
"Oh, I don't know, she just scares me. I've little wish to see her again!"
